{"id":1578,"date":"2021-07-21T17:23:30","date_gmt":"2021-07-21T17:23:30","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/?page_id=1578"},"modified":"2022-05-30T23:48:12","modified_gmt":"2022-05-30T23:48:12","slug":"necrotizing-soft-tissue-infection","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/necrotizing-soft-tissue-infection\/","title":{"rendered":"Necrotizing Soft Tissue Infection"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-page\" data-elementor-id=\"1578\" class=\"elementor elementor-1578\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-section-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-237806f elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"237806f\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-24d83c2\" data-id=\"24d83c2\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8178bf5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"8178bf5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h1 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Skin & Soft Tissue: Necrotizing Soft Tissue Infection (NSTI)<\/h1>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-3fb9b3c elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"3fb9b3c\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-cc88e83\" data-id=\"cc88e83\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8fa06ee elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"8fa06ee\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Necrotizing Soft Tissue Infection (NSTI)<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-908f54e elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"908f54e\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-7f01a5b\" data-id=\"7f01a5b\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-aa295e8 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"aa295e8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Definitions\/Variations<\/strong><\/p><ul><li><em>Necrotizing Soft Tissue Infection (NSTI)<\/em>: Necrotizing Infection of the Skin &amp; Soft Tissue<ul><li>Most (75%) are Polymicrobial<\/li><li>Most Common Monomicrobial Organism: Group A Streptococcus (GAS)<\/li><li>Includes the Other Variations Below<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><em>Necrotizing Cellulitis<\/em>: Necrotizing Infection of the Skin<ul><li>Spare Fascia &amp; Deep Muscle Compartments<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><em>Necrotizing Fasciitis<\/em>: Necrotizing Infection that Spreads Along Fascia Deep to the Subcutaneous Tissue<ul><li>Less Blood Supply Along Fascial Planes Allow More Rapid Spread of Bacteria Before Skin Changes are Seen<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><em>Necrotizing Myositis<\/em>: Necrotizing (Non-Clostridial) Infection Extending into the Deep Muscle Compartments<ul><li>Most Common Organism: Group A Streptococcus (GAS)<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><em>Clostridial Myonecrosis (Gas Gangrene)<\/em>: Necrotizing Clostridial Infection Extending into the Deep Muscle Compartments<ul><li>May Not Have Cellulitis<\/li><li>Most Common Organisms: Clostridium perfringens (Traumatic) &amp; Clostridium septicum (Non-Traumatic)<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><em>Fournier\u2019s Gangrene<\/em>: Necrotizing Infection of the Perineum<ul><li>Most are Polymicrobial<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Classification of Necrotizing Fasciitis<\/strong><\/p><ul><li><em>Clostridial Infection<\/em><ul><li>Usually Associated with Myonecrosis<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><em>Non-Clostridial Infection<\/em><ul><li>Type I: Polymicrobial<\/li><li>Type II: Monomicrobial<ul><li>Organisms: <strong>Group A Streptococcus (Most Common)<\/strong>, Staphylococcus aureus &amp; MRSA <a class=\"button\" style=\"background-color: #193556; padding: 2px 7px; border-radius: 2px;\" href=\"#MN\">Mn <\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Type III: Marine Bacteria (Vibrio)<\/li><li>Type IV: Fungal (Candida)<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Prognosis<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Rapidly Progress<\/li><li>High Mortality (25%)<\/li><li>Disfigurement &amp; Disability Can Be Considerable<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Risk Factors<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Trauma<\/li><li>IV Drug Use<\/li><li>Surgery<\/li><li>Obesity<\/li><li>Alcoholism<\/li><li>Immunosuppression (Diabetes, Cirrhosis, HIV)<\/li><li>Mucosal Brach (Hemorrhoids, Rectal Fissure)<\/li><li>Malignancy<\/li><li>Nonsteroidal Anti-Inflammatory Drugs (NSAIDs) \u2013 Debated<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Presentation<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Severe Pain (Out-of-Proportion)<\/li><li>Erythema (Without Sharp Margins)<\/li><li>Edema<\/li><li>Bullae or Ecchymosis<\/li><li>Crepitus<ul><li>From Anaerobic Production of Nitrogen\/Hydrogen Not Readily Absorbed by Tissue<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Visible Skin Necrosis<\/li><li>Hypoesthesia (Decreased Sensation)<ul><li>Late Finding from Small Blood Vessel Thrombosis &amp; Superficial Nerve Destruction<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Fever<\/li><li><strong>Murky Gray (\u201cDishwater\u201d) Fluid Drainage<\/strong><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-b5a838c\" data-id=\"b5a838c\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-13aab61 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"13aab61\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-12086 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/NSTI.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" srcset=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/NSTI.jpg 500w, https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/NSTI-300x224.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/p><p>NSTI of Abdominal Wall <sup>1<\/sup><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0ab6fac elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"0ab6fac\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-12084 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Necrotizing-Fasciitis.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"376\" srcset=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Necrotizing-Fasciitis.jpg 500w, https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Necrotizing-Fasciitis-300x226.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/p><p>Necrotizing Fasciitis <sup>2<\/sup><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7bcb8aa elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"7bcb8aa\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-12068 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Fournier-Gangrene.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"479\" height=\"374\" srcset=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Fournier-Gangrene.jpg 479w, https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Fournier-Gangrene-300x234.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 479px) 100vw, 479px\" \/><\/p><p>Fournier&#8217;s Gangrene <sup>3<\/sup><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-35cdde1 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"35cdde1\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-170565a\" data-id=\"170565a\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a8d60d1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"a8d60d1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Diagnosis<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Diagnosis is Only Confirmed by Surgical Exploration<\/li><li>Radiology \u2013 Soft Tissue Gas, Fluid Collections &amp; Inflammatory Changes<ul><li>CT Scan is the Best Initial Imaging<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><em>LRINEC Score<\/em><ul><li>\u201cLaboratory Risk Indicator for Necrotizing Fasciitis\u201d<\/li><li>Factors:<ul><li>CRP:<ul><li>&lt; 150 mg\/L: 0<\/li><li>\u2265 150 mg\/L: +4<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>WBC:<ul><li>&lt; 15 Cells\/mm<sup>3<\/sup>: 0<\/li><li>15-25 Cells\/mm<sup>3<\/sup>: +1<\/li><li>&gt; 25 Cells\/mm<sup>3<\/sup>: +2<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Hemoglobin:<ul><li>&gt; 13.5 g\/dL: 0<\/li><li>11-13.5 g\/dL: +1<\/li><li>&lt; 11 g\/dL: +2<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><strong>Sodium:<\/strong><ul><li>\u2265 135 mmol\/L: 0<\/li><li>&lt; 135 mmol\/L: +2<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Creatinine:<ul><li>\u2264 1.6 mg\/dL: 0<\/li><li>&gt; 1.6 mg\/dL: +2<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Glucose:<ul><li>\u2264 180 mg\/dL: 0<\/li><li>&gt; 180 mg\/dL: +1<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Interpretation:<ul><li>Low Risk (0-5): &lt; 50%<\/li><li>Intermediate Risk (6-7): 50-75%<\/li><li>High Risk (8-13): &gt; 75%<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Specific but <strong>Poor Sensitivity \u2013 Should Not Be Used to Rule Out<\/strong><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-70578d9\" data-id=\"70578d9\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-058fb5b elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"058fb5b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-7748 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/NSTI-XR2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"667\" srcset=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/NSTI-XR2.jpg 500w, https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/NSTI-XR2-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/p><p>Soft Tissue Gas on XR<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e1a8157 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"e1a8157\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-12069 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Fournier-Gangrene-CT.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"389\" height=\"247\" srcset=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Fournier-Gangrene-CT.jpg 389w, https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Fournier-Gangrene-CT-300x190.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 389px) 100vw, 389px\" \/><\/p><p>Fournier Gangrene on CT <sup>4<\/sup><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-f48e187 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"f48e187\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-546e534\" data-id=\"546e534\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-07246b4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"07246b4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Treatment<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Primary Treatment: <strong>Emergent Aggressive Surgical Debridement<\/strong> &amp; Empiric Antibiotics<ul><li>May Require Repeat Debridement Every 1-2 Days<\/li><li>Extremities May Require Amputation<\/li><li>Treat with Serial Wet-to-Dry Dressing Changes (May Consider Using Dakin\u2019s Solution)<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Empiric Antibiotic Regimen: Piperacillin-Tazobactam or Carbapenem Plus Vancomycin &amp; Clindamycin<ul><li>Broad Spectrum Coverage:<ul><li>Piperacillin-Tazobactam (Zosyn)<\/li><li>Meropenem (Merrem)<\/li><li>Ertapenem (Invanz)<\/li><li>Imipenem<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Vancomycin \u2013 Adds MRSA Coverage<\/li><li>Clindamycin \u2013 Inhibits Ribosomal Exotoxin Synthesis<ul><li>Panton-Valentine Leucocidin (PVL)<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>*Deescalate Based on Intraoperative Cultures<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Adjunct Therapies:<ul><li>Hyperbaric Oxygen Therapy<\/li><li>Intravenous Immunoglobulin (IVIG)<\/li><li>Plasmapheresis<\/li><li>Consider Diverting Colostomy for Severe Perineal Infections<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-0f672cb\" data-id=\"0f672cb\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-18211e2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"18211e2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-12070 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Fournier-Gangrene-Debridement.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Fournier-Gangrene-Debridement.jpg 500w, https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Fournier-Gangrene-Debridement-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/p><p>Aggressive Surgical Debridement <sup>5<\/sup><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-0567e57 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"0567e57\" data-element_type=\"section\" id=\"MN\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-1df9e0e\" data-id=\"1df9e0e\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9921930 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"9921930\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor